channel.title: "Your account has not logged out from its last session. [Close please <3]
channel.description:
I've been trying to login for a few minutes now, was wondering if anybody is experiencing this problem. I have a bank pin and JUST changed my pass for security reasons.
Edit: I guess my account was just nulled because I logged on and nothing was missing, not even my sara sword equipped. <3
Feel free to close now mods
